        "subject": "Twój folder Google Drive jest gotowy",
        "html": "=<!doctype html>\n<html lang=\"pl\">\n<head>\n  <meta charset=\"utf-8\">\n  <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1\">\n  <title>Folder Google Drive</title>\n</head>\n\n<body style=\"margin:0; padding:0; background-color:#f4f6f8; font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color:#202124;\">\n  <table role=\"presentation\" width=\"100%\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"width:100%; background-color:#f4f6f8;\">\n    <tr>\n      <td align=\"center\" style=\"padding:32px 16px;\">\n        \n        <table role=\"presentation\" width=\"100%\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\"\n          style=\"width:100%; max-width:620px; background-color:#ffffff; border:1px solid #e0e3e7; border-radius:12px;\">\n          \n          <tr>\n            <td style=\"padding:32px 32px 16px 32px;\">\n              <div style=\"font-size:13px; font-weight:bold; letter-spacing:0.6px; text-transform:uppercase; color:#5f6368;\">\n                Google Drive\n              </div>\n\n              <h1 style=\"margin:12px 0 0 0; font-size:26px; line-height:1.3; color:#202124;\">\n                Twój folder jest gotowy\n              </h1>\n            </td>\n          </tr>\n\n          <tr>\n            <td style=\"padding:0 32px;\">\n              <p style=\"margin:0 0 16px 0; font-size:16px; line-height:1.6; color:#3c4043;\">\n                Dzień dobry\n                {{ $('Webhook').first().json.body.firstName ? ' ' + $('Webhook').first().json.body.firstName : '' }},\n              </p>\n\n              <p style=\"margin:0 0 16px 0; font-size:16px; line-height:1.6; color:#3c4043;\">\n                przygotowaliśmy folder dla firmy\n                <strong>{{ $('Webhook').first().json.body.companyName }}</strong>.\n              </p>\n\n              <p style=\"margin:0 0 24px 0; font-size:16px; line-height:1.6; color:#3c4043;\">\n                Folder jest udostępniony w trybie tylko do odczytu. Możesz przeglądać znajdujące się w nim pliki, ale nie możesz ich edytować ani usuwać.\n              </p>\n            </td>\n          </tr>\n\n          <tr>\n            <td align=\"center\" style=\"padding:4px 32px 28px 32px;\">\n              <table role=\"presentation\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\">\n                <tr>\n                  <td align=\"center\" bgcolor=\"#1a73e8\" style=\"border-radius:8px;\">\n                    <a\n                      href=\"https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/{{ $('Create share folder').first().json.id }}\"\n                      target=\"_blank\"\n                      style=\"display:inline-block; padding:14px 24px; font-size:16px; font-weight:bold; line-height:1; color:#ffffff; text-decoration:none; border-radius:8px;\"\n                    >\n                      Otwórz folder\n                    </a>\n                  </td>\n                </tr>\n              </table>\n            </td>\n          </tr>\n\n          <tr>\n            <td style=\"padding:0 32px 24px 32px;\">\n              <table role=\"presentation\" width=\"100%\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\"\n                style=\"width:100%; background-color:#f8f9fa; border-radius:8px;\">\n                <tr>\n                  <td style=\"padding:16px;\">\n                    <p style=\"margin:0 0 8px 0; font-size:13px; line-height:1.5; color:#5f6368;\">\n                      Jeżeli przycisk nie działa, skopiuj poniższy adres i wklej go do przeglądarki:\n                    </p>\n\n                    <p style=\"margin:0; font-size:13px; line-height:1.5; word-break:break-all;\">\n                      <a\n                        href=\"https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/{{ $('Create share folder').first().json.id }}\"\n                        style=\"color:#1a73e8; text-decoration:underline;\"\n                      >\n                        https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/{{ $('Create share folder').first().json.id }}\n                      </a>\n                    </p>\n                  </td>\n                </tr>\n              </table>\n            </td>\n          </tr>\n\n          <tr>\n            <td style=\"padding:20px 32px 32px 32px; border-top:1px solid #e8eaed;\">\n              <p style=\"margin:0; font-size:13px; line-height:1.6; color:#80868b;\">\n                Wiadomość została wygenerowana automatycznie. Prosimy na nią nie odpowiadać.\n              </p>\n            </td>\n          </tr>\n\n        </table>\n\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  </table>\n</body>\n</html>",
